  Kian3-tiok kau3-hoe7 
  Hoe7-chiong3 tui3 tek-cho7, chha5-cho7, eng7 chhau2 lai5 kham3 e5 pai3-tng5 na7 u7 boan2-chiok lai5 kong2, chian3-au7 e5 kian3-siat pi2-kau3-tek bo5 siaN2 bun7-te5 ti7-teh. Chai7 Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 tiong-kan u7 chit8 koa2 hoe7-oan5 hian3 chhai5-liau7, iah8 soa3 theh8 lai5 kau3 ui7. Lau7-lau7 chiN2-chiN2, tak8 e5 chham-ka kang-chok. Hu7-jin5-lang5 chiong in e5 soe3-kiaN2 he7 ti7 ng2-nih, in pun2-sin iah8 oa2-lai5 chham-ka kian3-tiok8 e5 kang-chok. Iok chit8 le2-pai3 ku2 i2-lai7 kian3-tiok e5 kang chiu7 oan5-seng5. In tai7-ke put-tan3 oa2-lai5 pang-bang5 hou7 pai3-tng5 tit-tioh8 sit8-hian7 na7-tiaN7, soa3-chiap tui3 chit khoan2 e5 kau3-hoe7 iah8 u7 heng3-bi7 kap phah-boe7-li7 e5 thiaN3-sim ti7-teh; chit ho7 heng3-bi7 kap thiaN3-sim si7 in tui3 pat8 hang7 su7 sou2 boe7 thang kam2-kak-tioh8 e5. 
