  Chiah-e5 kiam2 si7 hiah-e5 chhu2 lang5-thau5-khak e5 mah? 
  Teng2-bin7 i2-keng kong2-khi2 liau2, Sun Sian-siN ti7 1946 ni5 e5 chhun-thiN tng2-lai5 Tai5-oan5 liau2-au7, u7 khi3 tang-hai2-hoaN7 khoaN3 ko-san tong5-pau ti7-chian3-si5 an2-choaN2 koe3-jit8 e5 su7. I kong2 i ti7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 koe3 chit8 e5 le2-pai3-jit8, ia7 hit jit8 u7 ti7 han3-jin5 e5 kau3-hoe7 chham-ka gou7 pai2 e5 le2-pai3-sek. Ji5-tong5 le2-pai3 kap teng2-pou seng5-jin5 le2-pai3 i2-au7, pai3-tng5 lai7 u7 kui2-na7 pah mia5 e5 Thai3-ia5 tong5-pau che7 kau3 boan2-boan2, in si7 liong7 chin3-cheng5 lai5 ti7 pai3-tng5 goa7 teh tan2-hau7 in e5 un5 e5. In che7 moa2 thong-lou7 i2-kip8 pai3-tng5-thiaN boe2-bin7 e5 khang-ui7. In si7 iau, chhui3-ta, him-bou7 gi7, hou7 lang5 in3-siong7 chin chhim e5 hoe7-chiong3; sin-khu iong2-chong3, hou7 jit8 phak8 kau3 ou-ma7-ma7, bin7-nih u7 chhiah hoe-ji7, bak8-chiu ou-lui2-lui2, oe7 chhak8 thau3 mih8-kiaN7. In tiong-kan choe7-choe7 lang5 chhiu2-nih u7 toa3 phoa3-noa7, siN-kou e5 Seng3-keng kap Si-chheh. Hiah-e5 chheh chiau3 khoaN3 si7 bat he7 ti7 goa7-bin7 ku3-chai7 hou7 ak koe3 e5 khoan2. Hiah-e5 chheh ui7-tioh8 sim2-mih8 in-toaN thai3 oe7 hiah au-chau leh? In-ui7 hiah-e5 chheh bat siu7 un2-khng3 ti7 goa7-bin7 nih, ti7 chioh8-tong7 nih, a2-si7 ti7 kui-tui e5 chhiu7-hioh8 nih; u7 si5 ia7 bat siu7 tai5 ti7 thou5-nih; che si7 beh siam2-pi7 Jit8-pun2 keng2-chhat, ng3-bang7 in lai5 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 ka-teng5 chhiau mih8 e5 si5 m7-bian2 hou7 in chhiau-tioh8. Mui2 pun2 e5 Seng3-keng na7 hou7 keng2-chhat hoat-kian3-tioh8, chiu7 but8-siu pang3 hoe2 sio. Hian7-si5 chiah-e5 Thai3-ia5-chok8 sou2 u7 e5 Jit8-bun5 Seng3-keng pi2-kau3-tek chin chio2, ia7 Seng3-keng oat8-ju2 chio2, oat8-ju2 po2-poe3. Chit e5 su7-sit8 tek8-piat8 u7 hah8 chit ku3 oe7 e5 i3-su3: “Chu2 e5 oe7 ti7 hiah-e5 jit8-chi2 si7 po2-kui3 e5.” 
  Sun Sian-siN khoaN3-tioh8 in bo5 khoaN3 chheh teh gim5-si, put-chi2 gong5-ngiah8. In teh gim5-si, u7-e5 u7 khoaN3 chheh, u7-e5 eng7 oat8-liam7. Na7-si7 ko3-ko3 e5 siaN-im hiang2-liang7 koh khoai3-lok8, long2 si7 tui3 kam2-sia7 e5 liam7-thau5 hoat-chhut e5. Hit e5 siaN-liong7 u7 toa7-toa7 poaN5-koe3 chin3-cheng5 ti7-hia le2-pai3 e5 han3-jin5 hoe7-chiong3 e5 siaN-liong7. In-ui7 chiah-e5 lang5 si7 sin e5 sin3-tou5, chin hoaN-hi2, chin hiap8-tiau, saN-kap teh gim5 kau3-hoe7 e5 ku7 Si. Lan2 beh tui3 lang5 kong2, in cho3-hoe2 oh8 gim5-si iau2 be7 kui2 geh8-jit8, a2-si7 kong2, in tiong-kan u7 lang5 choe3 Ki-tok-tou5 iau2 be7 loa7 ku2; che si7 hou7 lang5 chin oh-tit li2-kai2 e5 su7. Sun Sian-siN u7 chit8 ku3 oe7-bu2 tauh8-tauh8 khioh khi2-lai5 teh liu7 kong2, “Chiah-e5 kiam2 chin-chiaN3 si7 chhu2 lang5-thau5-khak--e5 mah? Chiah-e5 kiam2 si7 hiah-e5 hou7 lang5 chheng-cho3 chhiN-hoan--e5 mah? ” Chai7 in e5 seng-oah8-chiuN7 sou2 hian2-chhut e5 kai2-pian3, chiu7-si7 Sun Sian-siN sou2 bat khoaN3-tioh8 e5 choe3-toa7 cheng3-ku3 e5 chit8-e5, thang cheng3-beng5 hok-im u7 leng5-lek8 thang kai2-cho7 jin5-sim. 
  Kang2-to7 e5 si5-kan kau3 e5 si5, Thai3-ia5 tong5-pau e5 tiong-kan u7 lang5 theh8 pit-ki3-phou7 kap giah8 ian5-pit chhut-lai5 teh-beh pit-ki3. Theng5 chit8 tiap8-a2-ku2, u7 chit8 e5 siau3-lian5 e5 hu7-lu2 ka7 Sun Sian-siN kong2, i na7 tng2-khi3 hiuN-li2 e5 si5 tioh8 chiong sou2 thiaN e5 kong2 hou7 hiah-e5 in-ui7 lou7 hng7 boe7 tit lai5 e5 lang5 thiaN. U7 chit8 e5 si3-mia5 a2-si7 gou7-mia5 e5 sio2 thoan5-the2, ui7-tioh8 beh khi3 hia le2-pai3, tioh8 kiaN5 saN-chap8-gou7 eng-li2 e5 soaN-lou7. In ti7 pai3-gou7 e7-tau3 khi2-sin, pai3-lak8 kiaN5 kui jit8 lou7, kau3 le2-pai3-jit8 cha2-khi2, ti7 tu2-ho2 e5 si5-kan kau3 ui7. In lai5, bo5 tu2-tu2 si7 ui7-tioh8 beh thiaN hit ji7-chap8 hun-cheng ku2 e5 kang2-to7, iah8 m7-si7 beh koaN2-kin2 tng2-khi3 hu3 le2-pai3-jit8 e5 tiong-tau3 png7. Le2-pai3 soah, in koh lau5 toa3 hia gian2-kiu3 Seng3-keng, lian7-sip8 si-tiau7. In na7 bo5 kui-jit8 tiam3 ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 chhu3, sim chiu7 boe7 boan2-chiok. 
  Siang-teng5 e5 chap-ji7 su3-tou5 
  Sek-jim7 e5 soan-kau3-su but8-sek pian7 e5 si5, chiu7 chek-si5 ti7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 pak-hng e5 tang hai2-hoaN7 khai-siat chit8 keng Seng3-keng hak8-hau7, siat-pi7 nng7-ni5 che3 e5 kho3-theng5 lai5 hun3-lian7 thoan5-kau3-chia2. Ka-na2-tai7 TiuN2-lo2-hoe7 e5 Soan-to7-hoe7 u7 tit-tioh8 Ma2 Sian-siN kap Sian-siN-niu5 (Mr. and Mrs. Macllwaine) ji7-ui7 lai5 hong7-hian3 chit e5 kang. In si7 tui3 Jit8-pun2 lai5 e5 soan-kau3-su; u7 chiau-bou7 ji7-chap8-si3 mia5 chian5-tou5 iu2-ui5 e5 chheng-lian5, lai5 khai-si2 chit e5 kang-chok. Chit chou ti7 1948 ni5 6 geh8 pit-giap8, si7 tui3 ji7-chap8-it mia5 Thai3-ia5-chok8, nng7 mia5 A-mi-chok8, i2-kip8 chit8 mia5 Sai3-siat-chok8 lai5 chou-seng5 e5. In tiong-kan chap8-lak8 mia5 i2-keng siu7 chi2-phai3 ti7 tok8-lip8 kau3-hoe7, ia7 poeh mia5 khi3 boe7 siat kau3-hoe7 e5 sou2-chai7. Iau2 u7 leng7-goa7 chit8 chou ji7-chap8-chhit mia5 e5 chheng-lian5, si7 tui3 si3 chok8 e5 tiong-kan khioh chhut--lai5 e5, hian7-kim i2-keng jip8-oh8 liau2. Hian7-si5 ka3 chheh si7 eng7 Jit8-gu2 cho3 tiong-sim, na7-si7 chiong-lai5 oe7 koh siuN7 leng7-goa7 e5 pan7-hoat. Chit chhit chok8 e5 hong-gian5 oe7 liam5-piN siat-hoat eng7 bun5-ji7 lai5 piau2-hian7, ia7 ng3-bang7 pou7-hun7-tek e5 Seng3-keng oe7 tit chhut-pan2. Tui3 Bu2-lun2-chok8 thoan5-siu7 sin-sek e5 Lo5-ma2-ji7 e5 kho3-pun2 i2-keng in3 ho2. Che chiu7-si7 tui3 Bu2-lun2-chok8 e5 hong-gian5 sou2 chhut-hian7 thau5 chit8 pun2 e5 keng-tian2. 
  Tu2-chiah khai-si2 siu-seng5 na7-tiaN7 
  Ko-soaN e5 kau3-hoe7 chu7 khi2-chhou chiu7-si7 choe3 kian3-cheng3 e5 kau3-hoe7. Hiah-e5 sin3 Hok-im e5 lang5 liam5-piN tui-kiu5 beh tit-tioh8 pat8-lang5. Thoan5 Hok-im e5 kang-chok, si7 tui3 hiah-e5 peh-siN3 sin3-tou5 lai5 chin3-heng5--e5. In ui7-tioh8 beh tui3 pat8-lang5 kong2 to7-li2, u7 hian3 in e5 si5-kan, bou7-hiam2 in e5 siN3-mia7. U7 e5 ti7 hng5--nih teh choe3-kang e5 si5 tit-tioh8 in e5 peng5-iu2 lai5 sin3 Chu2. Iah u7 choe3 sin-niu5 e5 lang5 tit-tioh8 in e5 ang-sai3 lai5 jip8-sin3. U7 chit8-e5 choan-bun5 teh saN-ian2 e5 lang5, tui3 i e5 chi2-be7 e5 in2-chhoa7 lai5 sin3 Chu2. Chu7 hit-tiap8 i2-au7, bo5-lun7 khi3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7 saN-ian2 pi2-sai3, i u7 eng7 toa7-khui3-lat8 thoan5 Hok-im, chiu7-si7 kap kun-ong5 i2-kip8 chiang2-koan5--e5 teh saN-ian2. In in-ui7 u7 chit-khoan2 oah8-kian3-cheng3 ti7--teh, sou2-i2 bo5-ku2 e5 tiong-kan to7-li2 chiu7 thoan5-jip8 pat8-chok8. Thoat-li7 keng2-chhat it-chhe3 e5 han7-che3, Chu2 e5 oe7 u7 tit-tioh8 peng5-than2 e5 lou7 kap eng5-kng. 
  Chian3-cheng cheng5, chai7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 e5 A-mi-chok8 u7 khah lim2 chit8 taN2 e5 Ki-tok-tou5. Hit ui7 cho3 in e5 leng2-siu3 e5 chheng-lian5 siu7 keng2-chhat phaiN2 khoan2-thai7, lou7-boe2 siu7 tiau3 ka-jip8 Jit8-pun2 kun. Chu7-chai7 ti7 Hiong-kang2 e5 si5, i u7 kap chit8 e5 Sai3-siat-chok8 e5 chheng-lian5 chiap-chhiok; chit ui7 chheng-lian5 si7 tui3 san-te7 (hoan-kai3) e5 sai pak peng5 hia siu7 tiau3 khi3 e5. Chit e5 siong-hoe7 e5 ki-hoe7, kiat-ko2 u7 tit-tioh8 hit ui7 Sai3-siat chheng-lian5 lai5 sin3 Chu2. I ti7-chian3-au7 tng2-lai5 e5 si5, ti7 in e5 tang5-chok8 tiong khai-si2 kang-chok. Chit nng7 ui7 chheng-lian5 piN5-piN5 u7 jip8 Seng3-keng hak8-hau7, hian7-si5 choan-kang teh thoan5-to7. 
  Bu2-lun2-chok8 tui3 lan2 e5 thoan5 hok-im u7 piau2-si7 jiat8-liat8 e5 hoan-geng5. Tiam3 ti7 Li2-lang7 e5 thau5-lang5 ka7 Sun Sian-siN kong2 i e5 kiaN2 bat siu7 phian-jip8 Jit8-pun2 e5 kun-tui7, siu7 phai3 loh8-khi3 lam5 Thai3-peng5-iuN5. Jit8-pun2 lang5 ka7 in kong2 in na7 thai5-su hou7 lang5 liah8-khi3 e5 si5 lian5-hap8-kun oe7 thai5-si2 in, soa3 chiah8 in e5 bah. Au7-lai5 i e5 kiaN2 hou7 lang5 liah8-khi3 e5 si5, i put-chi2 gong5-ngiah8, in-ui7 bo5 siu7 lang5 khou2-chhou2, tian-to3 siu7-tioh8 chhin-chhiat e5 thai7-gu7. U7 chit8 ui7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 i-seng ti7-liau5 i e5 siong-jiah, tui3 i hian2-chhut i3-goa7 e5 gau5 khoaN3-kou3. I tng2-lai5 u7 tui3 san-te7 long2-chong2 e5 Bu2-lun2 tong5-pau kong2-khi2 chit e5 tai7-chi3. Tui3 chit ui7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 i-su sou2 hian2-chhut e5 chhin-chhiat u7 cho7-chiaN5 chit8 e5 chin toa7 e5 in3-siong7, chiu7-si7 pi2 lian5-hap8-kun sou2 u7 e5 chian3-lam7 kap eng-cha3-ki koh khah toa7 e5 in3-siong7. Hit ui7 thau5-lang5 kong2, “Goa2 taN chai-iaN2 peh8-bin7 lang5 m7-si7 goan2 e5 tek8-jin5 lah, goa2 chin ai3 goa2 e5 tong5-pau long2-chong2 chiaN5-cho3 Ki-tok-tou5.” 
  Toa3 ti7 lam5-pou7 hiah-e5 u7 khui3-lat8 e5 Pai5-oan-chok8 kau3 taN iau2 si7 chin oh-tit-thang chiap-chhiok e5. Chong2-si7 kang7-khoan2 e5 ki-hoe7 teh tan2-hau7 lan2 ti7-chia thoan5 hok-im. Ti7 choe3-kun7 choe7-choe7 pai2 e5 chip8-hoe7 tiong, u7 chit8 pai2, hoe7 beh kiat-sok e5 si5, u7 chit8 e5 chin u7 se3-lek8 e5 thau5-lang5 khia7 khi2-lai5 kong2, “Kin-a2-jit8 lan2 thau5 chit8-pai2 thiaN-tioh8 chit e5 ho2 siau-sit. Goa2 si7 lau7-lang5, chong2-si7 chu7 goa2 cho3 gin2-na2 kau3 chit-tiap8 ui5-chi2, goa2 boe7 bat thiaN-tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 chit khoan2 e5 siau-sit. Lan2 kin-a2-jit8 sou2 thiaN e5 ki3-jian5 si7 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 su7, goa2 u7 taN2-sng3 beh chiap-lap8 i, goa2 chin ai3 khoaN3 goa2 e5 tong5-pau iah8 long2 chiap-lap8 i.” 
  Sin-tek e5 han3-jin5 bok8-su kap i e5 kiaN2 ti7 san-te7 e5 sai-peng5 Kap-pan2-san e5 toe7-hng khai-si2 kang-chok. Ti7 chit e5 toe7-hng siang7 te7-it u7 se3-lek8 e5 ko-san-chok8, chiu7-si7 chit8-ui7 siN3 Lim5 e5 i-seng i2-kip8 chit8-ui7 hu7-lu2 kio3-cho3 Li2 Goat8-kiau. Ti7 lian5-siok8 kui2-na7 pai2 e5 chu7-hoe7--nih, in nng7 lang5 in-ui7 tam-tng thong-ek8 e5 koan-he7, sou2-i2 tui3 hok-im chiu7 siN-khi2 heng3-chhu3. Chong2-si7 in nng7 lang5 bat kui2-na7 ni5 ku2 kam2-cheng5 bo5 tu2-ho2. Ti7 lou7-be2 hoe5 e5 chu7-hoe7, u7 chit8 pai2 in nng7 lang5 long2 chhut-sek8, thiaN-tioh8 Ni5-ko-ti2-bo2 e5 kou3-su7 kap Chu2 e5 beng7-leng7 “Lin2 tioh8 teng5-thau5-siN” hit ku3 oe7. Keh tng2-jit8 thau3-cha2, Li2 Goat8-kiau khi3 hit ui7 i-seng hia, ka7 i kong2, “Lan2 tioh8 lai5 teng5-thau5-siN, tai7-ke koh lai5 teng5 phah-khi2, ke3-khi3 e5 su7 long2 pang3 hou7 boe7 ki3-tit, taN lai5 saN-kap oah8 ti7 Ki-tok-kau3 e5 to7-li2.” Ti7 hit jit8 e5 thiN-kng-cha2, in nng7 lang5 chiu7 ho5-kai2. I2-au7 ke3 boe7 loa7 ku2, hit ui7 i-seng i5-choan2 khi3 Tai5-pak, ti7 san-te7 oe7-seng-kho3 hok8-bu7. Li2 Goat8-kiau iah8 khi3 Tai5-pak, siu7 hun3-lian7 teh beh cho3 choan-jim7 e5 thoan5-kau3-chia2. Hit e5 i-seng choe3-kun7 u7 lai5 chhe7 i, ka7 i kong2, “Goa2 boe7 tit li2-kai2 ti7 li2 e5 sin-chiuN7 sou2 hian2-chhut e5 pian3-chhian, in-ui7 li2 goan5-lai5 koan3-si3 lim chiu2, chiah8 hun, me7 phaiN2 chhui3, siong7-chhiaN2 seng3-te7 iah8 chin oe7 kiaN lang5; m7-ku2 li2 hian7-si5 oan5-choan5 pian3-khoan2 lah.” I oe7 tit tui3 i kong2-khi2 chit e5 pian3-chhian e5 li2-iu5; in-ui7 i hian7-si5 “ti7 Ki-tok si7 sin chhong3-cho7 e5 lang5,” phau7 sin e5 jin5-seng-koan. Tai7-ke teh ng3-bang7 chit ui7 u7 leng5-lek8 e5 hu7-lu2 oe7 thang chiaN5-choe3 te7-ji7 e5 Chi-oang2, hou7 Siong7-te3 eng7, thang ti7 sai-hai2-hoaN7 lai5 choe3 ui2-tai7 e5 kang-chok, chhin-chhiuN7 Chi-oang2 ti7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 sou2 choe3 e5 chit8-iuN7; in-ui7 i u7 beng5-hian2 e5 kian3-cheng3 ti7-teh, ia7 hit e5 kian3-cheng3 chiu7-si7 eng7 i e5 sit8-te7 keng-giam7 choe3 te7-ki e5. 
  Chai7 Bu7-sia7 e5 sou2-chai7, iah8 u7 Thai3-ia5-chok8 tiong7-iau3 e5 tiong-sim ti7-hia. Bu7-sia7 e5 ui7-ti3 si7 ti7 in e5 hun-pou3 te7-tai3 e5 sai-lam5 kak. Tui3 Bu7-sia7 khoaN3 loh8 ke7 e5 sou2-chai7 chiu7-si7 Pou-li2 ko-goan5, hia u7 han3-jin5 e5 i5-bin5-thoan5 hoan5-eng5 e5 long5-hng5. Hia e5 han3-jin5 kau3-hoe7 e5 Bok8-su Lo5 Bun5-hok, hian7-si5 hian3 i e5 si5-kan, ti7 chit e5 toe7-hng teh cho3 soan-to7 e5 kang-chok. Cha2-si5 toa3 ti7 Bu7-sia7 hiah-e5 chhu2 lang5-thau5-khak--e5, tauh8-tauh8 chau2 loh8-lai5 piN5-iuN5, chng3-jip8 han3-jin5 e5 toe7-kai3, iah8 koaN7 chit8-koaN7 lang5-thau5-khak tng2-khi3. Chong2-si7 chiah-e5 cha2-si5 si7 ia2-ban5 lang5 e5 kiaN2-sun Bu7-sia7 tong5-paum chit-tiap8 loh8-lai5 piN5-iuN5, khiok m7-si7 ui7-tioh8 kau-chian3, si7 ui7-tioh8 beh choe3 le2-pai3, chiu7-si7 beh kap han3-jin5 saN-kap o-lo2 Siong7-te3, lai5 hoaN-hi2 “Sin3 chit8-e5, Chu2 chit8-e5” e5 kau-poe5. 
  Tak8 sou2-chai7 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 sin ki-hoe7 teh phu5-thau5 khi2-lai5 lah. Ko-san-chok8 e5 choan5 te7-kai3 teh chiaN5-cho3 chit8 khu e5 hng5, “pian7-pian7 thang theng3-hau7 siu-seng5” lah. 
  I-liau5 e5 su7-giap8 iah8 si7 chin toa7 khiam3. Jit8-pun2 keng2-chhat teh koan2 ko-san-chok8 e5 si5, in u7 po2-chhi5 chit8 keng, a2-si7 nng7 keng e5 si-liau5-iN7. Chong2-si7 chai7 chit e5 sin si5-tai7 khiok bo5 ui7-tioh8 chiah-e5 kho2-lin5, hou7 lang5 khoaN3 bo5 tioh8 e5 peh-siN3 siat-pi7 poaN3 hang7 hah8-eng7 e5 i-liau5 su7-giap8. Chhin-chhiuN7 eng5-iong2 put-liong5, hi3-piN7, koaN5-jiat8 cheng3, thang5-lui7, chit kui2 chiong2 e5 piN7-thiaN3 chin seng7-heng5, ia7 choe7-choe7 gin2-na2 ui7-tioh8 chiah-e5 piN7-thiaN3 chin siu7-khou2. Sou2-i2 i5-tong7-seng3 e5 chin2-liau5 ki-koan si7 choat8-tui3 pit-iau3--e5, ng3-bang7 chit kui2 hang7 e5 ban7-seng3 piN7 oe7-thang hian7-te7 tit-tioh8 ti7-liau5, ia7 khah siong-tiong7 e5 hoan7-chia2 thang sang3 khi3 kau3-hoe7 piN7-iN7 chiu7-i. 
  Thai3-ia5 tong5-pau teh sit8-heng5 chap8-hun7-chit8 e5 hong7-hian3 
  Ti7 choe3-kun7 e5 chit8 tiuN phoe nih, Sun Sian-siN sia2 kong2: “Chai7 Tai5-oan5 e5 tang-hai2-hoaN7-nih sou2 u7 long2-chong2 e5 kau3-hoe7, tu5-khi3 chit8 keng i2-goa7, hian7-kim long2 si7 tok8-lip8 e5 kau3-hoe7. Hia e5 peh-siN3 chai7 to2-lai7 kiam2-chhai2 si7 siang7 san3--e5, m7-ku2 bok8-su kap tiuN2-lo2 u7 kek8-lek8 soan-thoan5 chap8-hun7-chit8 e5 hong7-hian3, che chiu7-si7 chit8 e5 hian2-tu3 e5 seng5-ko2 tat8-seng5 e5 pi3-koat. Chai7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 e5 sou2-chai7 han3-jin5 e5 kau3-hoe7 u7 chap8-it keng, ia7 ko-san-chok8 e5 tok8-lip8 kau3-hoe7 u7 chap8-lak8 keng. In iah8 u7 hak8-sip8 chap8-hun7-chit8 e5 hong7-hian3. Cheng5 le2-pai3 goa2 u7 tui3 chiah-e5 kau3-hoe7 e5 chit8 keng, chiap-tioh8 chit8 tiuN hoe7-phio3 kap phoe, teh kong2-khi2 in u7 tui3 hoe7-chiong3 toe5 chap8-hun7-chit8 e5 hian3-kim, ia7 hoe7-chiong3 u7 koat-gi7 ai3 beh chiong hit phit e5 chiN5 chong2-giah8 chap8-hun7-chit8 choe3 soan-thoan5 hok-im ti7 in e5 hoe7-goa7 e5 lou7-eng7. In ia7 sang3 goa2 chit8 tiau5 sia7-le2, in-ui7 goa2 u7 choe3 San-te7 Soan-to7-hoe7 e5 hoe7-tiuN2. Chit-tiau5 sia7-le2 chiu7-si7 teh tai7-piau2 chiah-e5 lang5 e5 cheng-sin5. In tui3 Seng3-chheh Kong-hoe7 iah8 u7 hian3-kim, iu7-koh ku7-ni5 bou2 sou2-chai7 cho3 chui2-chai e5 si5, in iah8 kam-sim lok8-i3 te5 chit8 pit chiN5 khi3 kiu3-che3 hia e5 Tai5-oan5 lang5.” 
  Goan2 e5 chou2-chong e5 sin3-giong2 
  “SaN-pah ni5 cheng5 Ho5-lan5 lang5 chiam3 Tai5-oan5 e5 si5, goan2 e5 lang5 chiu7 i2-keng chiaN5-cho3 Ki-tok-tou5 lah, chong2-si7 put-heng7, in thiat-the3 i2-au7, goan2 chiu7 sit-loh8 kap Ki-tok-kau3 saN chiap-chhiok e5 ki-hoe7. Hian7-si5 goan2 ai3 hok8-to3 goan2 e5 chou2-chong e5 sin3-giong2, chhiaN2 li2 lai5 chi2-to7 goan2, ho2 m7 ho2?” 
  Chit ku3 oe7 chiu7-si7 Chu-o3-chok8 e5 thau5-lang5 tui3 Lam5-pou7 Tai7-hoe7 e5 Gi7-tiuN2 Ng5 Bu2-tong Bok8-su sou2 kong2--e5. Ng5 Bok8-su chiu7-si7 te7-it chhu3 khi3 hong2-bun7 chit thoan5 e5 ko-san-chok8--e5; in chit thoan5 u7 saN-chheng lang5, si7 khia7-khi2 ti7 koan5 4000 chhioh e5 A-li2-san e5 soaN-phiaN5-nih. Khi3 hong2-bun7 e5 jit8-chi2, chiu7-si7 1948 ni5 12 goeh8 chhe-kau2, chu7 thau5-lang5 chhe lang5 lai5 kiu5 phai3 sian-siN e5 jit8 khi2, kau3 hit-jit8 ui5-chi2, oa2 u7 chit8 ni5 khah ke ku2. Chu-o3-chok8 u7 thiah-hui2 sin5-sia7, eng7 an2-ni lai5 kheng3-chiok tit-tioh8 kai2-hong3, iah8 u7 chun2-pi7 teh-beh thiaN Ki-tok-kau3 e5 to7-li2. Chong2-si7 gi7-tiuN2 chin bo5 eng5, in-ui7 chian3-au7 piN5-iuN5 han3-jin5 e5 kok kau3-hoe7 tioh8 teng5 kian3-siat, sou2-i2 chiu7 boe7-tit-thang eng3 in e5 iau-kiu5 phai3 lang5 jip8-khi3 hia thoan5 to7-li2 hou7 chit-chok8 e5 lang5. Sui-si7 an2-ni, au7-lai5 i u7 bian2-kiong2 jip8-khi3; che7 chit8 cham7 soaN-lou7 e5 he2-chhia, chiu7-si7 Jit8-pun2 lang5 sou2 kian3-siat thau3-kau3 lim5-tiuN5 e5 thih-lou7 e5. Tui3 hia sun7 eh8-eh8 e5 soaN-lou7, kiaN5 nng7 tiam2 cheng ku2 chiah kau3 hit e5 thau5-lang5 e5 chhu3. Ui7-tioh8 m7-bat Chu-o3-chok8 e5 gian5-gu2, chiu7 eng7 Jit8-gu2 kap thau5-lang5 kong2-oe7. I2-keng tui3 thau5-lang5 piau2 keng3-i3, gi7-tiuN2 kap i e5 kiaN2-ji5 kiat-chiaN5 peng5-iu2, kong2 Seng3-keng e5 kou3-su7 hou7 in thiaN, ka3 in oh8 gim5-si. Ia7-kan eng7 ‘Chin-oah8 Siong7-te3’ cho3 te5-bak8 tui3 in kang2-lun7, hou7 in ti7 sim-te2-nih tit-tioh8 chhim-khek e5 in3-siong7. Chu-o3-chok8 u7 hok8-sai7 chit8 ui7 cho7-but8 chu2 e5 sin5 kio3-cho3 Akemamyo. In sin3 i chiu7-si7 ban7-hang7 ngou2-kok e5 cho7-but8 chu2. Sou2-i2 in chit8 ni5 chit8 pai2, ti7 siu-seng5 soe2-a2 e5 si5, ku2-heng5 che3-tian2, chiong thau5-chui2 e5 ke2-chi2 hian3 hou7 chit ui7 hong-seng7 e5 sin5-beng5. An2-ni thang kong2, in tui3 Ki-tok-kau3 sou2 thoan5 “Cho7-but8 Chu2 Siong7-te3” chit tiau5 to7-li2 m7-si7 bo5 sou3-iong2; sou2-i2 in chiu7 hoaN-hi2 sin3, kong2, “Chit ui7 Siong7-te3 pi2 Jit8-pun2 lang5 e5 thai3-iong5-sin5 ke iaN5 chin choe7.” 
